Package org.openwms.core.configuration.app

package org.openwms.core.configuration.app
Contains Spring configuration files and other lifecycle relevant types.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.openwms.core.configuration
    Contains classes dealing with preferences belonging to the schema http://www.openwms.org/schema/preferences.
    org.openwms.core.configuration.api
    Contains types that belong to the public API of the component.
    org.openwms.core.configuration.config
    Contains Spring configuration mapping classes.
    org.openwms.core.configuration.impl
    Contains the internal implementation of the component.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    PreferencesApplicationListener
    A PreferencesApplicationListener.
    PreferencesDistributedConfiguration
    A PreferencesDistributedConfiguration is activated with the Spring Profile SpringProfiles.DISTRIBUTED that shall be activated when the service is deployed as a microservice, not packaged within a standalone application, to enable service discovery.
    PreferencesModuleConfiguration
    A PreferencesModuleConfiguration is the microservice default Spring configuration, active by default.
